name: Brad Pitt
biography: Oscar-winning **actor**. Starred in *Fight Club* and *Once Upon a Time in Hollywood*.

name: Daniel Craig
biography: Played **James Bond** in five films. Known for a *gritty* style.

name: Denzel Washington
biography: **Two-time Oscar** winner. Known for *Training Day* and *Fences*.

name: Jennifer Aniston
biography: Famous for her role as *Rachel* in **Friends**. Also a film star.

name: Jennifer Lawrence
biography: Known for *Hunger Games*. Won an **Oscar** for *Silver Linings Playbook*.

name: Morgan Freeman
biography: **Narrator** and actor in *Shawshank Redemption* and *Million Dollar Baby*.

name: Natalie Portman

name: Robert Downey Jr.
biography: Best known as **Iron Man**. Made a huge comeback in the MCU.

name: Tom Cruise
